# ====== COMMENTS FOR TEAM ======
# This .gitignore is comprehensive for the Literary Circle project
# Key things being ignored:
# 1. Environment variables (contains Supabase keys)
# 2. node_modules (dependencies)
# 3. Build outputs (dist/, build/)
# 4. IDE settings (.vscode/, .idea/)
# 5. OS-specific files (.DS_Store, Thumbs.db)
# 6. Logs and cache files
# 7. Temporary and backup files
#
# If you need to commit any of these files, you can:
# - Use `git add -f filename` to force add
# - Comment out the relevant line in this file
# - Create an exception with !filename